Need AISI D2.... Insist on BÖHLER K110. BÖHLER K110 possesses a unique combination of toughness, wear resistance and compressive strength, making it an ideal alternative to standard AISI D2 grades, when performance is key. We now stock BÖHLER K110 at multiple locations across Australia in a wide range of sizes and profiles. #bohler #toolsteel #toolmaking #wearparts #voestalpine #onestepahead

Did you know #EschmannTextures are part of the #voestalpine family? Get in touch if you require state of the art texturing solutions for your moulds. #tooling #toolmaking #injectionmoulding #toolsteel #onestepahead

Uddeholm Dievar - Now Available for Additive Manufacturing. Uddeholm Dievar, a proven material for hot work applications, is now available in powder form for Laser Powder Bed (LPBF) and Direct Energy Deposition (DED) applications. Uddeholm Dievar is available as powder for AM service providers and as printed parts for our customers via our additive manufacturing centers. Take your inserts to the next level with Uddeholm Dievar. #uddeholm #dievar #HPDC #injectionmolding #toolmaking #additivemanufacturing #3dprinting #voestalpine #onestepahead

Discover how we use our unique combination of materials expertise and state-of-the-art technologies to develop 3D printed tooling solutions for our customers. We offer these technologies to our customers here in Australia, so there's no better time to work with us on your next innovation project. Watch the video to find out more. #toolmaking #injectionmoulding #toolsteel #additivemanufacturing #3Dprinting #voestalpine #onestepahead

voestalpine Foundry Group (a leader in the production of cast products) are using 3D printing technologies to produce the next generation of Monoblock Impellers - reducing lead-times and improving quality. Our latest datasheet explains how this technology can be used to offer innovative solutions to voestalpine customers. #voestalpine #casting #sandcasting #energysolutions #3dprinting #additvemanufacturing #onestepahead

We now stock Uddeholm Mirrax ESR at multiple locations across Australia. Uddeholm Mirrax ESR possesses a unique combination of toughness, corrosion resistance, high polishability and the ability to reach uniform hardness levels throughout large cross sections. Uddeholm Mirrax ESR is specially developed and adapted for larger moulds and applications where contamination is prohibited eg medical applications.. Uddeholm Mirrax ESR is available in the following size ranges: Round → 115mm - 508mm dia Block → sections over 500mm sq (subject to availability) To find out more about the benefits of Uddeholm Mirrax ESR visit our website or contact your local Technical Sales Representative. #toolmaking #injectionmoulding #toolsteel #uddeholm #mirrax #voestalpine #onestepahead
